2653:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_usart.h ****   * @brief  Perform basic configuration of USART for enabling use in Asynchronous Mode (UART)
2654:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g0xx_ll_usart.h ****   * @note   In UART mode, the following bits must be kept cleared:
